_sText:
My second Jail map. It has now cool jail rooms for every prisoner.

File Includes: ba_jail_painz_v2.bsp and Readme.

File is pretty small, but i think the map is cool. =) (Map size is 2mb I think.. but WinRar made it smaller..I think..)

Map Includes:

-Pool and jumping towers.

-Bathroom (Lockers are not working for some reason.)

-CT Base.

-Spawn cells for every prisoner.

-Insulation cell. (For bad prisoner.)

-Short "Race". (Running race.)

-Cage thingy with boxes inside.

-Secret went under ground.

File includes Readme.
